column.Name: AgentID
column.lookupquery: SELECT TradePartnerID, TradePartnerName FROM uTradePartner WHERE Active = 1 ORDER BY TradePartnerName

column.Name: TradePartnerVendorId
column.lookupquery: SELECT TradePartnerVendorID, VendorName FROM uTradePartnerVendor ORDER BY VendorName

column.Name: SizeClass
column.lookupquery: SELECT Custom, Custom AS CustomName FROM pSizeClass WHERE Active = 1 ORDER BY CustomKey
